            <title>[LU-1079] investigate whether build/autoconf/Makefile.am is needed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1079</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Per the discussion in &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,2115,patchset=1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#change,2115,patchset=1&lt;/a&gt; there is a Makefile.am in build/autoconf/ which has questionable value as what&apos;s in it seems to be controlled by build/autoMakefile.am.toplevel.&lt;/p&gt;

